name: Tethera
description: Tethera (USTT) is a TRC20-compliant cryptocurrency designed for fast and secure transactions on the TRON blockchain. With a fixed supply and customizable features, USTT is ideal for use in decentralized applications, token-based ecosystems, and as a store of value. Built with transparency and efficiency in mind, Tethera ensures seamless integration and usability for its holders.
